Burna boy was obviously not so happy about Blac Chyna’s proposed visit to Nigeria to sell bleaching cream. Blac Chyna is partnering with Whitenicious by Dencia to roll out a beauty product called “Whitenicious X Blac Chyna Diamond Illuminating & Lightening Cream”. It goes for N90,750(250 dollars) per jar. The Afrobeat singer,  Burna boy, expressed his opinions via his social media page. Photo: Instagram Photo: Instagramboy Read More: Blac Chyna Partners With “Whitenicious By Dencia” In his post, he also said, “black is beautiful”. Image: Instagram